html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="IE=edge")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    link(href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css", rel="stylesheet")
    title Keyframe Films
    link(rel="icon", href="./img/Logo/LOGO-2021-TRANSPARENTE_Mesa de trabajo 1.png")
  body(class="bg-black")
    main(class="transition duration-500 bg-black")
      section(class="relative w-full h-screen flex justify-center items-center overflow-hidden transition duration-800")
        img(src="./img/Fotos Dron/Amanecer.jpg", id="bg", class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full object-cover pointer-events-none")
        h1#text(class="relative z-10 text-white text-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl animate-fade-in") KeyFrame Films
        img(src="./img/Logo/LOGO-2021-BYW_Mesa de trabajo 1 copia.png", id="logo", class="absolute top-0 left-20 w-72 sm:w-96 lg:w-108 xl:w-120 animate-fade-in")
      div.sec(class="relative min-h-screen py-20 px-10 md:px-20 lg:px-32 xl:px-40 animate-fade-in")
        div.hamburger(class="fixed top-5 left-5 z-50 transition-opacity duration-300 hover:opacity-50")
          div(class="w-10 h-1 bg-gray-300 my-1 rounded")
          div(class="w-10 h-1 bg-white my-1 rounded")
          div(class="w-10 h-1 bg-gray-300 my-1 rounded")
        nav.navbar(class="bg-gray-900 w-1/5 fixed top-0 left-0 bottom-0 z-50 hidden md:block animate-fade-in")
          ul#menu(class="overflow-hidden py-2")
            li(class="block w-full py-2 px-6 text-white hover:bg-red-500 transition duration-300")
              a(href="#Inicio") b Inicio
            li(class="block w-full py-2 px-6 text-white hover:bg-red-500 transition duration-300")
              a(href="#Portafolio") b Portafolio
            li(class="block w-full py-2 px-6 text-white hover:bg-red-500 transition duration-300")
              a(href="Paquetes/Paquetes.php") b Paquetes
            li(class="block w-full py-2 px-6 text-white hover:bg-red-500 transition duration-300")
              a(href="#Contacto") b Contacto
        div.content#Inicio(class="relative z-10")
          h2(class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-blue-500 mb-8 animate-fade-in") | En nombre de todo nuestro equipo,
            br
            | me gustaría darle la bienvenida a nuestro sitio web.
          p(class="text-white text-lg md:text-xl animate-fade-in") 
            | Nuestra productora se ha comprometido a ofrecer contenido cautivador, emocionante y de alta calidad desde sus inicios.
            br
            | Aquí encontrarás un espacio dedicado a la creatividad, la innovación y la ilusión por la producción cinematográfica y audiovisual.
            br
            br
            | ¡Esperamos que disfrutes de tu visita y que te emociones tanto como nosotros con nuestro apasionante universo cinematográfico!
        div#Portafolio(class="relative animate-fade-in")
          h2(class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-blue-500 mb-8 mt-20") Portafolio
          ul.galeria(class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center py-10")
            each image in ["../../public/img/Gastronomia/Don_Mundo_2.JPG", "../img/Retrato/Fatima12-4.jpg", "../img/Retrato/20.jpg", "../img/Retrato/13.jpg", "../img/Fotos Dron/Cielo Dron_.JPG", "../img/Gastronomia/Don_Mundo_Hamburguesas.JPG", "../img/Gastronomia/Don_Mundo_Entrada.JPG", "../img/Gastronomia/Don_Mundo_Tacos2.jpg"]
              li.galeria__item(class="w-full sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/3 lg:w-1/4 xl:w-1/5 p-2 animate-fade-in")
                img(src=image, class="w-full hover:grayscale-0 transition duration-500")
          script(src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.0/jquery.min.js")
    div#lastray.element
    script(src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.3.1/gsap.min.js")
    script(src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.3.1/ScrollTrigger.min.js")
